{"tid":1423232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"火系魔法師 麻煩入一入","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:16:18.000Z","uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b789196025c3b2a6c5aac5b04513fd5770699a8f","tid":1423232,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:17.000Z","msg":"自己p牌仔<br />\n但非分化撚，死也不割<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">火系魔法師</span></span>，琴日既火攻睇到大快人心<br />\n但係我先講，魔法唔好掉到車，植物，或者其他易燃易爆炸既野<br />\n絕對唔好掉到人/犬，唔可以有任何人/犬因為魔法 出現<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">死傷</span></span><br />\n燒到易燃易爆炸既野 會增加消防/救護哥哥既工作量<br />\n以及<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">最重要</span></span>既係，令轉緊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></span>既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">淺藍</span></span></strong></strong></span>同埋d<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">淺黃</span></span>割席<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>強調 強調 強調 強調 強調</strong></span></span><br />\n我地唔可以失去民心<br />\n加上文宣需要時間去宣傳魔法<br />\n大家要比d時間文宣 文宣組工作量都好大<br />\n希望大家可以暫時停止使用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">火系魔法</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069aa699707ba513f3faa652d57c6dc3e682cb58","tid":1423232,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:28:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ad8cf2398e2ce2f2d1afa66f9741f0b9159a220d","tid":1423232,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd231132090973496591674502ad78d2bd02dd7b","tid":1423232,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:16:18.000Z","msg":"文宣要時間 重講"}]}